          "value": null
        },
        "category": "defensive",
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>The fourth anchor.</strong> A skull and dust — <em>inert and unaware</em> while his remains lie undisturbed; he takes 1 round to fully wake (skull rising, ash vortexing) once they are. Immune to nearly everything; resistance all 15. <strong>Bloodless removal:</strong> a <em>dispel evil/dispel law</em>-grade casting or an antimagic effect severs the anchor without battle — but the attempt itself counts as disturbing his remains.</p>"
        },
